  "remarks": "Alexander Zverev is the CEO of JSC Zavod Dagdizel, which is a military industry company involved in developing and producing underwater weapons for the Russian Navy used in the war of aggression against Ukraine. JSC Zavod Dagdizel is a subsidiary of MPO-Gidropribor, which is part of JSC Tactical Missiles Corporation.",
